title: Jazz Crusaders - Live At The Lighthouse '66 (1966; 1996) [FLAC]
description:
The Jazz Crusaders - Live At The Lighthouse '66
Label: Pacific Jazz Records - CDP 7243 8 37988 2 7
Format: CD
Country: US
Released: 08 Jul 1996
Genre: Jazz
Style: Hard Bop, Soul-Jazz


Reissue of the 1966 release cat-# 20098.
Recorded live at The Lighthouse, Hermosa Beach, California on January 14-16, 1966.
Remixed from the original three-track tapes.
Tracks 5 and 6 are bonus tracks and were previously unreleased.
